Implement hiera_structutre fuction

It Allows us to make hiera queries into deep structures

$data = {
  'a' => {
    'b' => [
       { 'x' => 1 },
       { 'y' => 2 },
       { 'z' => 3 },
     ]
  }
}

hiera_structure('a/b/1/y', 'default_value') => 2

It can be very convenient with astute.yaml data.

